    "crystal_structure": null,
    "chain_flexibility_notes": "Common structural principle: glassy or semi-crystalline 'hard' domains act as physical (reversible, meltable) crosslinks holding together rubbery 'soft' domains -- unlike a chemically crosslinked thermoset rubber, a TPE can be re-melted and reprocessed.",
